      <title>富国银行利润超出预期，拨备减少，股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/wells-fargos-profit-falls-lower-interest-income-2024-10-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[得益于财富管理业务的韧性和信贷损失准备金的减少，富国银行第三季度的利润超出了分析师的预期，推动其股价在周五开盘前上涨了 3.5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/wells-fargos-profit-falls-lower-interest-income-2024-10-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 10:55:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通利润超出预期，得益于投资银行业务实力强劲、利息收入增加</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-profit-drops-bigger-provisions-loan-losses-2024-10-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通第三季度利润超出预期，因为强劲的投资银行业绩和不断增加的利息支付抵消了贷款损失准备金增加带来的冲击，导致其股价在开盘前上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-profit-drops-bigger-provisions-loan-losses-2024-10-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 10:53:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
